== symbol table handling ==
currently, all identifiers outputted same way in XML

extend handling of identifiers
- output category - var/local, argument, static, field, class, subroutine
  - if var/local, argument, static, field, output also running index assigned to var in symbol table
- output whether being defined or used

extend syntax analyzer with identifier handling described above
- using custom output/tags format
- test on project 10 programs
